videos.description: Texas Tech's Jahmi'us Ramsey fakes the shot, sidesteps and sinks a 3-point shot.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Ramsey pumps, sidesteps and drains 3-pointer) 2020/03/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ramsey pumps, sidesteps and drains 3-pointer

videos.description: Matthew Mayer cuts to the lane and Freddie Gillespie finds him for the Baylor score.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Gillespie dishes to Mayer for the Baylor bucket) 2020/03/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gillespie dishes to Mayer for the Baylor bucket

videos.description: Texas Tech's Davide Moretti passes up a wide-open jumper that leads to a turnover and score for Baylor's Matthew Mayer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Moretti's mistake leads to points for Baylor) 2020/03/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Moretti's mistake leads to points for Baylor

videos.description: Devonte Bandoo dishes to Freddie Gillespie on the pick-and-roll for the jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Gillespie rolls to the paint for the dunk) 2020/03/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gillespie rolls to the paint for the dunk

videos.description: Freddie Gillespie rises for a big-time block on the defensive end, which leads to a 3-pointer from MaCio Teague as the Baylor crowd goes wild.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Baylor crowd erupts following big time block, 3-pointer) 2020/03/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor crowd erupts following big time block, 3-pointer

videos.description: MaCio Teague hits a clutch step-back 3-pointer which ends up being the difference as Baylor defeats Texas Tech 71-68 in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Teague's step-back 3-pointer propels Baylor past Texas Tech in OT) 2020/03/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Teague's step-back 3-pointer propels Baylor past Texas Tech in OT
